 <span data-ttu-id="843dd-144">Anwendungen können den Wert von vollständig ändern <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextToSpeak%2A> .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="843dd-144">Applications are free to completely change the value of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextToSpeak%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="843dd-145">Wenn Sie den Wert von zurücksetzen, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextToSpeak%2A> wird der Wert von und nicht geändert <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextOffset%2A> <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextLength%2A> .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="843dd-145">Resetting the value of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextToSpeak%2A> will not change the value of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextOffset%2A> and <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextLength%2A>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
